  "title": "cleaning services manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Scheduling and deployment of cleaning manpower to assigned jobs/sites</li>\n  <li>Implement improvement initiatives to enhance operational efficiency</li>\n  <li>Developing, executing and ensuring company SOP's are complied with</li>\n  <li>Monitor and ensure smooth running of daily manpower operations, arrange for replacement of staff as and when necessary</li>\n  <li>Sending equipment and/or manpower to job sites as and when required</li>\n  <li>Buiding open and trusting relationship with clients to achieve long term partnership and contract renewal</li>\n  <li>Monitoring and upholding the cleaning and maintenance quality standards and operating procedures for all jobs/sites and surpass the clients' expectations</li>\n  <li>Conduct site visits and advise on manpower requirements and costing for jobs</li>\n  <li>Manage equipment and supplies inventory maintenance and replenishment as and when necessary</li>\n  <li>Oversee effective OJT training to maintain high standards of works</li>\n  <li>Managing overall staff motivation, discipline, development and performance according to the organizational, human resource and government manpower policies</li>\n  <li>Overseeing the assigned job sites according to manpower and site requirements to achieve profitability and cost-effectiveness</li>\n  <li>Resolving of feedback or complaints from clients and taking immediate preventive measures to ensure that similar problem does not resurface</li>\n  <li>Recruiting and interviewing applicants to maintain sufficient manpower</li>\n  <li>Facilitate compliance with regulatory requirements and Workplace Safety and Health policies, procedures and regulations</li>\n  <li>Assist the Management in preparing and maintaining documentation required for regulatory requirements</li>\n  <li>Assist at job sites as and when required</li>\n</ul>",
